g.inkscape:label: moon position relative to tree leaves

text.tspan: There are at least two different translations available:
Old pond, frog leaps in, sound of water
Old pond, frog leaps in, water's sound
"Sound of water" avoids a contraction and is
less ambiguous, but ultimately I switched to the
second one because it fits the word order of
the original better. The slightly shorter text
was also better for layout purposes.
